const core_scenario_data = {
    outcome_id: scenario.outcomeID || null,
    is_ill: scenario.is_ill || null,
    who_for: scenario.who_for || null,
    age: scenario.age || null,
    vaccine: scenario.vaccine|| null,
    gender: scenario.gender || null,
    transgender: scenario.transgender || null,
    latinx: scenario.latinx || null,
    ethnicity: scenario.ethnicity

        : null,
    life_threat: scenario.life_threat || null,
    cov19_contact: scenario.cov19_contact || null,
    cov_test_result: scenario.cov_test_result ||null,
    old_test_result: scenario.old_test_result ||null,
    cov_test_age: scenario.cov_test_age ||null,
    how_feel_old_test: scenario.how_feel_old_test ||null,
    symptom_severity: scenario.symptom_severity || null,
    covid_symptoms: scenario.covid_symptoms
        ? scenario.covid_symptoms.map(sym => ({ index: scenario.symptom_lists.COV_symptoms.indices[sym.index], entity: sym.entity }))
        : null,
    comorbidity: scenario.risk_factors
        ? scenario.risk_factors.map(risk => ({ index: scenario.symptom_lists.comorbidity.indices[risk.index], entity: risk.entity }))
        : null,
    nursing_home: scenario.nursing_home || null,
    healthcare_facility: scenario.healthcare_facility || null,
    ped_nursing_home: scenario.ped_nursing_home || null,
    school_dorm_daycare: scenario.school_dorm_daycare || null,
    ppe: scenario.ppe || null,
    close_contact: scenario.close_contact || null,
    covid_other_symptoms: null,
    ed_symptoms: null,
    _911_symptoms: null,
    breathing_symptoms: null,
    user_experience_consent: scenario.user_experience_consent || null,
    user_experience_helpful: scenario.user_experience_helpful ||null,
    user_experience_followrec: scenario.user_experience_followrec ||null

    
}

conversation.core_outcome = {
    core_scenario_outcomes: scenario.test_message_outcomes ? [...scenario.core_scenario_outcomes, scenario.test_message_outcomes] : scenario.core_scenario_outcomes,
    core_scenario_data
}

const log_outcome = {
    message_outcome: scenario.core_scenario_outcomes.map(outcome => outcome.replace(/msg/, 'MSG ')),
    test_message_outcome: scenario.test_message_outcomes.map(outcome => outcome.replace(/msg/, 'MSG ')),
    version: scenario.version,
    core_scenario_data
}

session.logCustomEvent('CDC_CORE_OUTCOME', log_outcome)
session.trace(log_outcome, 1)

// we need to trigger an outcome event for the messages before the last one
let mToOutcome = log_outcome.message_outcome.slice()

// if there is not a testing message outcome then the last message in the message_outcome array
// is the last message and will automatically be logged so we don't need to log that again so
// we remove it
if (!scenario.test_message_outcomes) {
  mToOutcome.pop() 
}

for (let outcome of mToOutcome) {
  session.logOutcomeEvent(outcome)
